Summary

Final system testing confirms that SmartPark is functioning as a complete full-stack application. The system supports database-backed login, role-based routing, parking recommendations, reservation and release functionality, admin parking lot management, and persistent MySQL storage through Docker.
All major features were tested successfully and are ready for the final project demonstration.
